{
  "stem": "11957.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] After this was all going on, there-- there was a Russian Partisan group over there formed itself.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the local population reported to the Russians that there is a Jewish group in your Partisans.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So one of the Russian leaders came over, and he asked him if he want to join them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So I and another fellow, Yoste Shuhart, joined them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were now under the Russian Partisans under the Russian command.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Whatever they had to do, we did it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So now you're officially unofficially a Partisan with the Russians?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mm-hm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we were blowing up bridges and blowing up [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] railroads that they were sending [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to the front, supplies to the front.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we were blowing it up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we didn't have to learn because it was already-- all they had to do was pull a string and that ignited the--",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Explosives.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the explosives were ready.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All you had to do was pull a string to ignite it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we picked a-- we picked a-- a spot where it would do the best damage for-- for the railroads.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we went there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We dug this under the railroad tracks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we stood back about 5,000 feet when-- when we heard a train going by that area.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we pulled the string and blew up-- blew up the track and the train.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, it felt very good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was dangerous work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's how I got my-- my nickname, Nieustrazony Rozpoznawczy, because I did not fear any-- anything they were sending me out to do, I went with pleasure to do it.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I got my nickname Nieustrazony Rozpoznawczy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That means fearless reconnaissance, fearless reconnaissance.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
